MX users dynamically joining IRC rooms on a server:
- Storage: Dynamically tracked channels
- Alias query -> Bot joins IRC room -> Adds to tracked channels list

MX users dynamically PMing an IRC user on a server:
 - Storage: Which room ID is the PM room for this tuple(mx,ircnick)
 - User query -> Bot joins server, /whois <nick>, if nick is online, then YUP.
 - Presence-like status for virtual mx user?
 - onInvite for irc user, join virtual mx user.
 - onMessage for PM room, mk virtual irc user then send.
